          <div class="hero-grid">
            <!-- left: copy -->
            <div class="hero-copy">
              <div class="landing-kicker">Local | Free | Opensource</div>
              <h1 class="hero-headline landing-heading-primary">
                Save tokens and extend your coding sessions.

              </h1>
              <p class="landing-copy mt-5">
              Command outputs and state recollection are the biggest sources of token overuse and context clutter.
              CtxSift is a skill to save tokens by keeping sessions clutter-free and helping agents recover state faster.<br>
              </p>

